text:
Se nota el oficio, en todo momento pendientes sin hacerse empalagosos, sin dudarlo el mejor servicio que he visto hasta el momento y creo que va a ser difícil de superar;  plato tras plato en orden y sin pausas a medida que lo vas terminando, adelantando tus necesidades sin tener que hacer gesto alguno. Por mucho incidir en ello no soy capaz de describir la enorme profesionalidad de todas y cada una de las personas que trabajan al servicio de este restaurante.
El local es bonito pero sin ser pretencioso y la calidad de lo servido muy acorde, en mi opinión, a lo ofrecido. Buena gente, buena calidad y mejor trato.

Si sirve de referencia, repetiría sin pensarlo.
textTranslated:
The expertise is evident, always attentive without being cloying, without a doubt the best service I've seen so far, and I think it will be hard to beat; dish after dish in order and without pausing as you finish, anticipating your needs without having to make a gesture. No matter how much I dwell on it, I can't describe the enormous professionalism of each and every one of the people who work at this restaurant.
The place is beautiful but not pretentious, and the quality of what is served is very consistent, in my opinion, with what is offered. Good people, good quality, and even better service.

If it's any guide, I would definitely come back.

text:
Hola, soy jose. Nos casamos mi mujer y yo el dia 21 de Junio, solo puedo decir cosas buenas.
El coctel fue en el jardin, esta muy bien cuidado al igual que la piscina.
La comida les llego a todo el mundo y con cantidad. Tambien hizo calor y no les falto a nadie que beber.
La comida calidad 100%, la gente repitio lo que quiso, los platos con muy buena presentación, nadie se quedo con hambre y ni con sed.
La atencion fue extraordinaria,el trato del personal inmejorable, estuvieron pendiente en cada momento de nosotros para que saliera todo bien.
Volveria a repetir ese dia 1000 veces mas y siempre seria alli, estoy muy feliz con ese restaurante, nos hicieron sentir en casa.
Tengo que agradecer la atencion al cocinero y como no, Amparo y Valle, sin ellas no hubiera salido todo genial.
Muchas gracias al equipo Montes.
textTranslated:
Hi, I'm Jose. My wife and I got married on June 21st. I have nothing but positive things to say.
The cocktail party was in the garden; it's very well maintained, as is the pool.
The food was plentiful and available to everyone. It was also hot, and everyone had plenty to drink.
The food was 100% quality; everyone had seconds, the dishes were beautifully presented, and no one left hungry or thirsty.
The service was extraordinary, and the staff was unbeatable. They were attentive to us at every turn to make sure everything went smoothly.
I would repeat that day 1,000 times and would always return there. I'm very happy with that restaurant; they made us feel at home.
I have to thank the chef for their attention, and of course, Amparo and Valle. Without them, everything wouldn't have turned out so well.
Many thanks to the Montes team.

We will visit you again; a place not to be forgotten.

text:
Buenos días, mi reseña no se puede basar en la calidad de la comida o servicio, sino en la música de sus eventos.

Podemos calificarla de variada y para todas las edades, el nivel de volumen bastante elevado superando los decibelios permitidos por ley y lo mejor hasta las 6 de la mañana o más.

Me parece de VERGÜENZA que se permita esto cada vez que haya un evento y NO se haga nada, los vecinos tenemos bebés, trabajos, viajes y estamos expuestos a este show cada vez que hay acontecimientos.

Un saludo
textTranslated:
Good morning, my review isn't based on the quality of the food or service, but rather on the music at your events.

We can describe it as varied and suitable for all ages. The volume level is quite high, exceeding the legally permitted decibels, and even better, it lasts until 6 a.m. or later.

I find it SHAMEFUL that this is allowed every time there's an event and nothing is done. Our neighbors have babies, jobs, travel, and we're exposed to this spectacle every time there's an event.

Best regards.

textTranslated:
I loved it. Fabulous service, spectacular atmosphere, the food service was perfect, everything arrived at the right time, and the food was a 10/10. We had a cold starter of Russian salad and hot starters of exquisite lobster croquettes, tempura vegetables, and battered prawns. For our main course, we had cod with Manchego-style ratatouille and fried leeks, and salmon with Japanese marinade, citrus, and pickles.

A spectacle of flavors! For dessert, we had French toast with white chocolate and coconut and mango rice pudding.
